raw_body: COLLINS LEO MILROY peacefully passed away on 9 Nov. 2023. Cherished husband of Lourdes,​ beloved father of Sharon,​ father-in-law of Eugene,​ son of late James and Emily,​ brother of late Ranjini,​ Sherwin,​ Desmond,​ Premilla & Nirupa,​ son-in-law of late Xavier & Agnes. Burial in Auckland on 14 November.074115
